Workplaces.name: Da Nang Tech Hub
Workplaces.overview: Centrally located in the coastal city of Danang, DNC- Danang Coworking space aims to create a vibrant hub for innovation & creative industry. We’ll suit your best needs by providing an inspiring workspace with modern facilities along with a close-knit community of like-minded entrepreneurs. Together with DNES-Danang Business Incubator, we are proud to be nominated asthe 3rd most creative spaces in Vietnam by British Council in 2018.
